by javiereguiluz at 2018-10-08T15:34:22Z

@Lreus thanks for this contribution! In theory, in Symfony 4.1 the right command is `./bin/phpunit` (this is created by the PhpUnitBridge recipe. See https://github.com/symfony/recipes/blob/master/symfony/phpunit-bridge/4.1/bin/phpunit)  Did you have some problem with this command? Doesn't . /bin/phpunit` work for you?

